## Lint checks

Run `/pin-llm-wiki lint` to check wiki health.

| # | Check | Severity |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Citation coverage — every factual claim has a chain to a raw file | ERROR (WARN on overview.md) |
| 2 | Contradictions — conflicting claims across pages | WARN |
| 3 | Orphan pages — no inbound `[[wikilinks]]` (includes overview.md and log.md) | WARN |
| 4 | Data gaps — concept in ≥`topic_min_products` (default 3) distinct products with no topic page | INFO |
| 5 | Missing cross-references — page mentions a wiki-known entity without linking | WARN |
| 6 | Stale sources — last refresh > 30 days | INFO |
| 7 | Terminology collisions — same term used for different concepts across sources | WARN |
| 8 | Frontmatter shape — source pages must NOT have `sources:` | ERROR |
| 9 | Citation path format — must be relative-from-file, not root-relative | ERROR |
| 10 | Inbox consistency — inbox line marked [x] but still under ## Pending | WARN |
| 11 | Adapter sync — `.cursor/rules/wiki-instructions.mdc` body and `.github/copilot-instructions.md` must match `AGENTS.md` | WARN (auto-fixed) |

Auto-fixes applied on every lint run:
- Missing `overview.md` / `log.md` links in `wiki/index.md`.
- Re-sync `.cursor/rules/wiki-instructions.mdc` and `.github/copilot-instructions.md` from `AGENTS.md` when Check #11 detects drift (preserves the Cursor file's YAML frontmatter).

Topic candidates from Check #4 are **reported only** by default (`topic_creation: report`) — promote them to real topic pages via the manual harvest flow below. Set `topic_creation: auto-stub` in `.pin-llm-wiki.yml` to restore the legacy behavior of auto-creating empty stub topic pages.

**Source independence:** Check #4 counts distinct *products*, not distinct sources. Sources sharing a `product:` frontmatter value (e.g. a marketing site + its own GitHub repo) count as one product, so a feature shared between them does not falsely trigger a topic candidate.

Checks #2 (contradictions) and #7 (terminology collisions) are deferred in Phase 1 — reported as informational notes only.

